{"schemaVersion":"gas-shunin-manual-law-explanation-audit/v1","reviewedAt":"2026-07-11","qualification":"gas-shunin-kou","examYear":2021,"sourceQuestionKey":"gas-shunin:kou:2021:law:q01","questionLabel":"問1","sourceQuestionBodyText":"法令で規定されているガス事業法の日的用語の定義等に関する次の記述のうち誤っているものはいくつあるか。","sourceFile":"output/gas-shunin-kou/questions_json/2021/00_source/question_2021_firestore_2.json","explanationPatchFile":"output/gas-shunin-kou/questions_json/2021/21_explanationText_added/question_2021_firestore_2_explanationText_added.json","sourceCorrectChoiceText":["間違い","正しい","間違い","正しい","正しい"],"patchedCorrectChoiceText":["間違い","正しい","間違い","正しい","正しい"],"correctChoiceTextMatchesSource":true,"choiceReviews":[{"choiceIndex":0,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["ガス事業法第1条"],"basisText":"保護する利益はガスの使用者の利益である。"},{"choiceIndex":1,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同法第2条第11項"],"basisText":"ガス事業はガス小売、一般ガス導管、特定ガス導管及びガス製造の各事業をいう。"},{"choiceIndex":2,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["同法第35条"],"basisText":"一般ガス導管事業を営もうとする者は経済産業大臣の許可を受ける。"},{"choiceIndex":3,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["ガス事業法施行規則第1条第2項第5号"],"basisText":"液化ガスは0.2MPa及び35度の条件により定義される。"},{"choiceIndex":4,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["ガス事業法第175条"],"basisText":"高圧ガス保安法の所定規定はガス事業及びガス工作物に適用しない。"}],"changedFields":["explanationText","sourceExplanationCommonSummary","sourceExplanationChoiceSnippets"],"result":"reviewed_and_rewritten","sourceUrls":["https://laws.e-gov.go.jp/law/329AC0000000051","https://laws.e-gov.go.jp/law/345M50000400097"]}
